  "monster": {
    "title": "Diosoekej.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Diosoekej has a muscular brown body and eerily human features. It looks diseased.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 197     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++ +   </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: +         </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ∞       </lightgrey><lightgrey>   rC: +..      </lightgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: +        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 180% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 90% to hit with the +9 demon whip of the Harvest.\nIt has about 21% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage    After Damaging Hits \nHit     55 (base 37)  Ensnare with webbing\n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to acid and corrosion and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
    "quote": "",
    "status": "<white>Strong:<lightgrey>\n   This creature's melee attacks deal 50% more damage.\n\n<white>Spells empowered:<lightgrey>\n   This creature's spells are strengthened and it will cast them more\n   frequently.\n\n<white>Unusually resistant:<lightgrey>\n   This creature's resistance to fire, cold, poison, electricity, and corrosion\n   are all increased by one level.\n\n<white>Sheltered from injuries:<lightgrey>\n   Half of the damage suffered by this creature is redirected to the ally\n   protecting it instead.\n\n",
